<p>In <xref ref-type="table" rid="table1-0954405412464484">Table 1</xref>, not only total cost (346,000) is distributed among activities by different percentages, but also activity cost rate is obtained based on the customer demand. Finally, total cost and total time for all activities are shown by summation cost and time of each activity.</p>
